{"tid":428529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本女記者加班159小時　最終過勞致死","createTime":"2017-10-08T06:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T05:24:48.000Z","uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c8cc72d9ae3568ab2720adec32e9e252b6f1ab91","tid":428529,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"日本新聞網報道，日本放送協會NHK的31歲女記者佐戶未和在2013年時候，一個月內加班159個小時，最終心臟病發作，在寓所死亡。東京都涉谷勞動基準監督署確認她是過勞致死。<br />\n<br />\nNHK公布，佐戶未和當年採訪東京都議會及參議院兩場選舉，在她死前1個月，加班159小時，只休息2日，到7月24日心臟病發作死亡。死者父母初時不希望公開女兒死因，但電通公司的1名年輕的女職員因為過度加班而抑鬱自殺，令他們醒覺要令外界關注過度加班的問題，因此要求NHK公佈女兒的死因。<br />\n<br />\n唔怪之得日本堆後生仔寧願做freelance 都唔做local 企業，外企就爭崩頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09eb27ac1a5c2c0fec3855d1b56447e0a6259bd6","tid":428529,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:07:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da8c3263a2c05030c92da8cc3e29c4ec3c12fa53","tid":428529,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"NHK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw又話日本工時低過香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fcb548ee991e2ba20d4388e416badbac34f114","tid":428529,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67c575d4639da46d5faa725981a0da33e1e543b","tid":428529,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"Asia haha"},{"pid":"4b76e7d7c59aba61484d4d1dbfaa29f716a21058","tid":428529,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"仲話移民"},{"pid":"ccc8128bf19ae9356387ae9f5575399961eb23c5","tid":428529,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"349f5b6e30c141